I feel so lost alone in this world again. I try to go on with a broken heart, but its so hard to forget that love i have. It burns with such anger yet, craves the love, attention it needs from a male. Everyone I see seems to be happy with someone they either like or love. Me I feel so broken, unloved, lost, forbidden to find another. It's like every time i start to like a guy he gets all weird an stops talking to me or tells me "oh i only like you as a friend." I don't know why but alot of people think I can get with any guy. I know it's sorta true but I just don't feel right. Something is wrong with me, with my life. I can't help but to get sad an very lonely. I guess I care so much of others that I tend to forget that I too am very lonely in life. I always try to make others happy when I should look at myself. Also alot of peoplt think I am very blonde or just don't have enough brains. When to be honest I have a lot of brains but i don't like to be smart cause a lot of the time you get used or you just are really smart.....I don't know. All I know is that I do have brains an just because I am blonde doesn't mean I have to be stupid. I know that the way I act makes me look weird or stupid but once you get to understand I am a very normal person with a loveing personality. I just hate how guys don't really give me that chance thye take one look an that's it. I hate that. But when I met "him" I was me inside an out. I had nothing to hide from him. What I showed him I could not show others. I showed him my love. Tell this day I do still love him very much but, I don't show it anymore. Something happened that I cannot explain nor tell myself. All I know is that since November 15, 2004 I lost a big chunck of myself. I have changed from once a happy loving young lady to a bitter old bitch. An so I wonder what it was that has left? Could it be my heart that was once full of hope an love? Or my other half that was full of great good, happieness, love, an lost of spirtit? well i have to go so i will be back later

Memories (part 3)
the memories that i have for you will NEVER go away. When we were together at Carl's Jrr. You would play games with me. you'd play feeties try to tickle me any way of holding me in your arms. Knott's Scary Farm was the best you got me scared by making monster noisies in my ear. You carried me on you shoulders for about 20mins. On the way home was the best being held by you i went ot sleep. Every where we went you always held me so close afride you loose me. Now that things are gone you lost me. I would do just about anything to start over. Because i learned that if you dont have a friendship first you wont last in a relationship. Yes i have so many fon memories but they can only bring me more pain then wat is needed i cant go things go places with out seeing a memorie of us. Take this one Carl's Jr. I go ther all the time but you alway came to my mind. Why is that? Because we were there every damn day. I haven't been to Knott's sice we were their. To be honset all i have of you is a picture and my memories. We had so much fun together. We would hang out every day. We called each other none stop. Every day you'd kiss me hello, good-bye, an for the hell of it. I remember one time you called me at 7pm we talked tell 10:30pm you thought that if you hung up you would lose me. Wat happen instead i lost you. I dont ever want to lose you or the memories. But on days like this you leave me no choice but to try an forget it all. My memories make me happy but can bring me pain an sarrow. One thing i remember is you said you would never leave me. But you did you did leave me. You also told me you would never hurt me but you did you left me with out saying good-bye or even why? But i know within your own fun loving memories you will never let me go that why you never said good-bye because you love me. an i love you.
I'm better off on my own (part 4)
I tryed to be perfrect but that wasnt good enough for you. I said i give you my heart an i did but now that i want it back you wont give it to me. i tryed to be perfect but it just want worth it. So i am better off on my own. I still love you an always will but it takes two to complet an for now tell things go better i am going to be better off on my own. I dont need  you dragging me down by playing wiht my emotions. You know that i love you and would do anything. Now that i see the way you treat me i wont give into any of your bull shit games. You flirt wiht her in fron of me an then she tell's me, "oh i only do it to make you upset." But i know that she lies cause she always talkes about you & your best friend. I see the way you look at her. You have the looks you use to give me. But im better off on my own. I dont know if things will ever go back to us but i hope that we would at least make an attempt to be my friend. I lost you once but i wont lose you as a friend you mean a lot to me. I wont forget the times we had but i want to make times for us to be friends. There is one thing if i go on my ownt i will nit g=forget you or the love you an i had togehter. i think you should here the song Pieces by Sum 41. Im not sure if that the song but its a song you should hear then think about me an the words, "I've tryed to be perfect but it just wants worth it nothing could ever be so wrong its hard to beleive me it never gets easy i guess i knew that all along. If you believe its in myself in all the words i know just to see if it would show that im trying to let you know that im better off on my own." Thats the chours but either way that is how i feel a lot of the time. I am trying to also let you know that i am letting og to be better off on my own. Please if you care jutst a tiny bit in your heart try to understand i tryed to be perfect but it wasnt worth it so i am better off on my own. Thereis one thing i wont leave is the look we had this morning when we both open oppostie doores the look of love/hate for one another. Before i go to be better off on my own. Wat are you going to do now that yor the nice guy whos gonna finish last when you run outta gass. lol Nice guys finish last- Green Day. There's so many songs you should hear that remind me of you. Like Sum 41 over my head ( better off dead ) i hope that things will go better if we talk this all out togheter. Becoming friends might help us both understand one another once again. But maybe im better off dead or on my own. " I'm falling an now I'm in over my head with something i said i'm better off dead. " I hope you understand this you asshole. I'm better off on my own. But i still love you.
